					<description><![CDATA[<p>Are you on the right track with your SEO? These statistics will help guide your strategy.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/seo-statistics">101 SEO Stats to Reference Everywhere in 2025</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
